verbose_text: However, in the hemocytes of LvIAP2 silenced shrimp, the expression of LvALF1 was upregulated 1.97- and 17.08-fold at 24 and 36 hpi, respectively (XREF_FIG); the expression of LvALF2 was upregulated 1.65- and 3.13-fold at 24 and 36 hpi, respectively (XREF_FIG); the expression of LvALF3 was upregulated 15.00- and 123.87-fold at 24 and 36 hpi, respectively (XREF_FIG).
